<l>karappiṭumpai yillāraik kāṇi ṉirappiṭumpai </l>
<l>yellā moruṅku keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>All the evil of begging will be removed at the sight of those who are far from the evil of refusing.</l>
